48
00:02:40,547 --> 00:02:42,299
Personal little quirk.

49
00:02:42,973 --> 00:02:45,362
- You don't mind, right?
- Not at all.

50
00:02:45,650 --> 00:02:47,561
Good.

51
00:02:47,824 --> 00:02:51,533
