151
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:04,514
Yeah, that's smart. Keep pushing me.

152
00:09:08,608 --> 00:09:13,238
- Did you see that?
- Yeah, he took my ice cream.

153
00:09:23,371 --> 00:09:25,362
Hey, neighbor.

154
00:09:26,549 --> 00:09:27,948
Hi, Rose.

155
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:31,968
- Didn't you have dessert with Sherri?
- How did you know I was with Sherri?

156
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:35,153
