Double-booking.

164
00:09:57,162 --> 00:09:58,481
You practically invented it.

165
00:09:59,713 --> 00:10:02,944
No, she wouldn't do that to me.
Why would she do that to me?

166
00:10:03,268 --> 00:10:06,419
Did she do that to me?
She did that to me, didn't she?

167
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:11,020
- Excuse me?
- Sorry.

168
00:10:11,256 --> 00:10:13,850
