a little selfish delight in your pain.

169
00:10:14,142 --> 00:10:15,939
The Germans call it "schadenfreude"...

170
00:10:16,191 --> 00:10:18,625
but here in the U.S.A.,
we just go:

171
00:10:22,422 --> 00:10:24,777
- Thanks.
- Oh, Charlie...

172
00:10:25,057 --> 00:10:28,652
you don't need a girl like that.
You could do so much better.

173
00:10:29,783 --> 00:10:31,580
