out of my head?

177
00:10:39,945 --> 00:10:44,655
Okay, that's not where I was going,
but let's review:

178
00:10:45,048 --> 00:10:48,757
She's gorgeous,
but she's also self-centered...

179
00:10:49,104 --> 00:10:51,538
