231
00:14:02,319 --> 00:14:05,277
What's short, picky and only
supposed to be here on weekends?

232
00:14:05,581 --> 00:14:08,015
I'll give you a hint: It's your kid.

233
00:14:09,219 --> 00:14:10,937
I know. I know.
